MEDITATE: Restore PPE or ISP

Syntax: meditate

DESCRIPTION:
  Enter meditation to recover psychic or magical energy. Psionic OCCs restore
  ISP. Magic OCCs restore PPE when standing on a ley line.

NOTES:
  Meditation has a cooldown of about ten minutes.
  Psionic users restore ISP based on level.
  Magic users must be on a ley line to draw PPE.
  ISP also recovers slowly over time and faster while resting.

SEE ALSO: rest, psionics, psi, score
